{"tid":642490,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(少量圖透慎入)(男主勁)有冇ching有睇過套中世紀幻想系漫畫 「雷恩」","createTime":"2018-04-25T21:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T12:20:37.000Z","uid":6327,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c20a1036130a9dc80dceaa587f5501fca4e65102","tid":642490,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T21:50:16.000Z","msg":"今次呢套去到今日為止 漫畫有87話出左<br />\n個故仔都係講國家紛爭+英雄主義+d奇幻式陰謀野<br />\n套野好睇在班配角 姐係男主班手下慢慢變勁<br />\n男主雖然係屈曬機但真係有原因....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會有一種審美疲勞  慢慢好多秘密浮現<br />\n表面嘻嘻哈哈 但係......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054524_8cf50d4fd2b6e418b2854a15d800ff74.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054524_8cf50d4fd2b6e418b2854a15d800ff74.png&h=100d653d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/052758_b628d7678de59d87fbd2785a421c29c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F052758_b628d7678de59d87fbd2785a421c29c7.png&h=046371fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/052218_93f2dcde9ce3f6d19129eb00461d664d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F052218_93f2dcde9ce3f6d19129eb00461d664d.png&h=67817d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個女主角公主又話係小綿羊 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/052024_37a0240618c50a2631dd6dba472570f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F052024_37a0240618c50a2631dd6dba472570f8.png&h=c8bafca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解黑起上黎可以黑到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然係第二人格<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/052025_b89e03526a8f2d6dc22ce19a5bad8e7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F052025_b89e03526a8f2d6dc22ce19a5bad8e7b.png&h=a4cce46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢位係配角黎<br />\n但個名有小小似我老友<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/052902_47f98f2f332d9e7f7a1a83ed106aa977.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F052902_47f98f2f332d9e7f7a1a83ed106aa977.png&h=705c9248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我主要想講呢套d女女好岩我胃口<br />\n黑頭髮既女仔相比之下 真係比班異色頭髮女屌打(外貌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054022_2acebebae873f4aabe3a7b124e17163d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054022_2acebebae873f4aabe3a7b124e17163d.png&h=cf24062d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054023_eb4643abba686f66592fbd3b44ceb4ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054023_eb4643abba686f66592fbd3b44ceb4ed.png&h=7e2b0433&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054024_08508a7a9b61a9aea9340a2802e7a768.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054024_08508a7a9b61a9aea9340a2802e7a768.png&h=c2425af8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054025_c119bdd78364ed922a1ad5067d5b4808.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054025_c119bdd78364ed922a1ad5067d5b4808.png&h=35d8e0a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/054026_4b098a602af6ecf3e98771f3dcb5dc39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F054026_4b098a602af6ecf3e98771f3dcb5dc39.png&h=6d82ce1f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49638b4a546534843a2dc4ece99a79ea0f601c9b","tid":642490,"uid":10652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T23:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de40eb19cd7766fd05dfb76a67196a985839927e","tid":642490,"uid":70505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:04:28.000Z","msg":"好似好一般"},{"pid":"84800b4a2b8567143afced6dca2d000a064dc112","tid":642490,"uid":6327,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"de40eb19cd7766fd05dfb76a67196a985839927e","tid":642490,"uid":70505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:04:28.000Z","msg":"好似好一般"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"講唔出d咩大道理 <br />\n不過我覺得畫得d女靚 <br />\n故仔冇咩暴走既長篇算係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又可以睇d強大型男主同反派<br />\n有人投訴我成日推介d漫畫成日都短過閪<br />\n終於搵到套長小小既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7d296aeb962a218cd1c50876e64486430e7293","tid":642490,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"細個係圖書館借過小說睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcb248b977188394791d979203e674e3fbc40fa","tid":642490,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"記得個男主角好似係弒龍者 好鬼勁"},{"pid":"97f035b002788c41ae7a6ffd4ece1505dc89c5ec","tid":642490,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"635f3f99d18bab326890031108e90f332d55ff22","tid":642490,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dcb248b977188394791d979203e674e3fbc40fa","tid":642490,"uid":125203,"like":0,"dislike